      • getPointBarriers

        public final com.google.gwt.core.client.JsArray<Point> getPointBarriers()
        The point barriers are an array of points. They are returned only if ServiceAreaParameters.returnPointBarriers was set to true (which is not the default). If you send in the point barriers as a featureSet (instead of using DataLayer), you already have the barrers and might not need to request them back from the server.
        Returns:
        JsArray
